data.description: With a fabulous McCandless location, a newer metal roof, and a great yard, this home has so much to offer! The living room offers a log burning fireplace and access to the covered side porch. The dining room is open to the living room and to the updated kitchen which includes granite counter top, tile backsplash, smooth surface range, and access to the rear patio. Main level master w a private full bath with tile shower. Two upper level bedrooms each have built-in shelving. The upper level full bath includes a tub with tile surround. An entrance from the driveway opens to the large game room with adjacent half bath. The laundry room includes a washer, dryer, and built-in cabinetry. A large pantry/storage room is connected to the walk-out home office. The rear yard is certain to be a favorite place to be with a large patio, built-in barbeque, fenced yard, updated storage shed, an above ground pool with updated liner and a newer saltwater filtration system. Close to everything!
